    {
      "id": "e3ea18d3-b154-4460-970f-dcfb79ce0b68",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Thus, the authors use Deep Learning from video clickstream data to understand how a student will perform on a given week of the MOOC. Authors use LSTM for this purpose and find that the approach outperforms all other baseline models used - with accuracies ranging between 82% and 93%. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "e3ea18d3-b154-4460-970f-dcfb79ce0b68",
        "parent": {
